{"tid":2456637,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"設計師承認暴動今判囚3年9個月，黑官：一人做錯全家都要承擔","createTime":"2021-03-22T05:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T12:44:27.000Z","uid":211994,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1452abd54a005d828ddc7029fe535cb03830ad13","tid":2456637,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"法官咁講係咪即係支持黑警死全家？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/UKXRCQJZS5FX5PPKFOLNPS6LGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FUKXRCQJZS5FX5PPKFOLNPS6LGI%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=ebd6e2eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FUKXRCQJZS5FX5PPKFOLNPS6LGI%2F&h=6b47e05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/UKXRCQJZS5FX5PPKFOLNPS6LGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地出生的產品包裝設計師，前年8月5日全港大三罷當日在黃大仙龍翔道堵路現場站在示威者前線，向防暴警揮舞雨傘及投擲頭盔，其後欲拾起催淚彈殼企圖掟回警方時被捕。事件中一名督察被人用彈叉鋼珠射爆門牙。<br />\n<br />\n設計師被控暴動罪，上周臨開審前承認控罪，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">法官陳廣池</span></span></strong>指暴動刑罰不能單看個別參與者的行為作判斷，必須考慮被告所協助的那群人的所作所為，又指「一個人犯事並不是一人當，而係整個家庭、所有深愛犯案者嘅人都要承擔。」考慮到被告獲家人強大支持重新做人，酌情減刑，終判即時監禁3年9個月。"},{"pid":"32acd6161e523628a81b62196b4b5b56007fcfbb","tid":2456637,"uid":296866,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"法官支持黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98240e0c567d856b4aa5c87eba42439f16c8c351","tid":2456637,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39627c39d8243174b7b3a74c71077d83d33ea518","tid":2456637,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0cd416d978b4aeba5539f08545864ca2b4686e","tid":2456637,"uid":11291,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"個官間接認同黑警死全家"},{"pid":"c90a58b6f447caf67d1bca330bbd9a3709026a3a","tid":2456637,"uid":200638,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"公平講句 人地呢句係減刑原因呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />意思係罰太重係家人一齊承受 所以唔罰咁重<br />\n雖然黑警都係死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e53ec2b9efee528847861c78193db555eb755d","tid":2456637,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"委任司法人員<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  下稿代司法機構發出：<br />\n<br />\n  司法機構今日（三月三十日）宣布委任陳廣池先生為區域法院法官，任命由二○○七年四月二日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n  委任由行政長官根據司法人員推薦委員會的推薦而作出。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">  由於陳先生在獲委任前是律政司高級助理刑事檢控專員</span>，他在加入司法機構後的六個月內不會處理任何涉及政府的刑事審訊或民事案件。<br />\n<br />\n  陳廣池先生的簡歷如下：<br />\n<br />\n  一九五八年在香港出生。一九八六年及一九八七年分別取得香港大學法學學士學位及法學專業證書。一九八七年在香港獲大律師資格，同年加入當時的律政署為助理檢察官，一九八八年和一九九一年先後晉升為檢察官和高級檢察官，並於二○○二年晉升為副首席政府律師，同年出任高級助理刑事檢控專員。<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２００７年３月３０日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間１６時５０分<br />\n列印此頁"},{"pid":"44db44263b7ca1ec51829b01b1f47047e7cb0ef4","tid":2456637,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1452abd54a005d828ddc7029fe535cb03830ad13","tid":2456637,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"法官咁講係咪即係支持黑警死全家？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/UKXRCQJZS5FX5PPKFOLNPS6LGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FUKXRCQJZS5FX5PPKFOLNPS6LGI%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAf